  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To Evaluate the efficacy of Z-338 in subjects with Functional Dyspepsia, focusing on the
      assessment of subjective symptoms in order to further determine the optimal dosage and
      efficacy parameters for PhaseIII clinical trials.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
